7
00:00:21,359 --> 00:00:22,640
[SPEAKER_02] Ja to nikad nisam uspio.

8
00:00:22,800 --> 00:00:24,879
[SPEAKER_02] Meni je baba govorila da sam nježnjak u ežu.

9
00:00:27,280 --> 00:00:29,440
